QuestData.Title: Backed Into a Corner
QuestData.Description: The naga are upon us, $c. Aid us in fightin' dem off!
QuestData.LogDescription: Defend the Earthen Ring camp until the naga retreat.
QuestData.CompletionText: Dey seem relentless, but we gonna turn dem back!
QuestData.RewardText: I'm glad you were here, mon.$B$BToshe be lookin' like he wants to chase dem down. You should go help'em.
